{"tid":586979,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子貨車內燒炭 同事發現已太遲","createTime":"2018-03-10T04:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T04:48:21.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4d16296f8830405db3a747b0654628ac7ed39151","tid":586979,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180310/large/1520650782_3cca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180310%2Flarge%2F1520650782_3cca.jpg&h=42407288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子在車內燒炭自殺身亡，遺體被移落地面，警方封鎖現場調查。(詹家志攝)<br />\n<br />\n早上9時47分，停泊在葵涌葵裕街路邊的一輛密斗貨車，司機被發現昏迷車內，旁邊有燒過的炭。警方接報到場，打爛車窗，但證實事主已告不治，正調查其尋死原因。死者姓葉24歲，現場消息稱，事主昨晚取去公司貨車，至今早被同事發現他倒斃車內。警方找來一名女親友認屍。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180310/57927349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180310%2F57927349&d=RRtZKrgL7KbMpQD%2BJNyOfB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=cd36a85f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180310%2F57927349&h=b5226896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180310/57927349</a>"},{"pid":"9daf499f9c6f2b50bb0dcad2c935e0d25463ec0c","tid":586979,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:48:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}